Austria to Cut Costs Even Without Constitutional Debt Brake

-- B y   Z o e   S c h n e e w e i s s
-- 
2011-12-05T11:00:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-05/austria-to-cut-costs-even-without-constitutional-debt-brake.html
Austria ’s Finance Minister Maria Fekter said the country will cut costs even without a
constitutional debt brake.  “We will continue to work on a reform program,” Fekter
told reporters in Vienna today. “We will start a cost cutting
path to reduce deficits, because I consider it for incredibly
important that our finances stay stable.”  To contact the editor on this story:
Zoe Schneeweiss in Vienna at 
 zschneeweiss@bloomberg.net  